name: Ted Stafiej
text: Don't believe the broker, not open 24/7. Guys there are really cool. Got me unloaded asap.

name: Bob McCullough
text:
Whoever was driving your small Chevrolet flatbed truck south on I-65 today, July 22, 2016, around 1:15 PM near the Jefferson County line, is an idiot who should not be licensed.

Weaving in and out of traffic and speeding with your company name plastered down the side of your vehicle isn't good PR.
